description:
FOR THIS REASON is a fast-paced journey through the Scriptures of the prophets, the world’s best seller, the Bible. Beginning at creation, it unfolds the story of WHY the Creator-Owner of the world sent a Savior into the world, WHO He is, and WHAT He did to rescue His rebel subjects from the kingdom of darkness and qualify them to live with Him forever in His kingdom of light. Abridged from the 15-episode KING of GLORY movie, this one-sitting epic connects the dots of the Old and New Testaments, revealing how everything points to the One whose birth split world history in two. 

Director - P.D. Bramsen
